{"tid":1803074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人熟悉TwitterHelpBot？我有嘢想問","createTime":"2019-12-30T02:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T12:14:36.000Z","uid":71237,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"18141447e85819c071d4f432593485a69cb31b43","tid":1803074,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"我係「維基百科戰線」的成員之一，因為寫維基百科需要引用大量新聞報導，所以Twitter戰線每日收集新聞嘅工作對我們寫維基百科好有用。而家我會check住TwitterHelpBot嘅每日任務，睇下有咩可以擺落維基百科。<br />\n<br />\n我想請問有咩方法可以睇到TwitterHelpBot過去提供過嘅任務？或者我應該喺Twitter follow邊個先可以睇到最多嘅外國新聞？謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n題外話：如果想加入「維基百科戰線」，請閱讀下面依個post睇新手教學。<br />\n維基百科戰線招募長期參與者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1789084\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1789084</a>"},{"pid":"5e2d3704601034e438f78e51094bca8ed90bd63e","tid":1803074,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:01:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4eededda298a3dbf6170739a023090517277aa16","tid":1803074,"uid":179963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:03:04.000Z","msg":"每日都禁一次？"},{"pid":"eb31f22533d929a823edcda913b2a63dbc56f5fc","tid":1803074,"uid":179963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:04:04.000Z","msg":"寫bot果個人喺twitter文宣group入面，你可以問下佢"},{"pid":"c2fd6b759e4ffc79aac3e865c246f77d923f2ca8","tid":1803074,"uid":179963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T03:04:25.000Z","msg":"好似叫咩IOT"},{"pid":"b5ff4db34df92e02e977912e6a194de4536e725d","tid":1803074,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b40a425853f9d18858f262932e8409f058122ef1","tid":1803074,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5ff4db34df92e02e977912e6a194de4536e725d","tid":1803074,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:53:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T18:12:01.000Z","msg":"problem solved <im